               <person instant="false"><!--donor-->
                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">The parchment (branna) was donated by Wäldä Dawit (s. colophon). He and his wife Ṭǝʿǝmt Maryam were mentioned in supplication formulas (fols. 14rb, 105ra, 140ra, 168ra, 170va, 175ra, 193va, 196ra, 200vb, 201ra, 204rb, 220va). However, their names has been erased in the most cases and replaced with that of Wäldä Mikaʾel. &#xD;
Other persons mentioned are Kǝflä Giyorgis (fol. 109ra), Ḫadärä Giyorgis (fol. 113ra) and Kǝflä Maryam (fols. 189va, 197va).&#xD;
Mälkä Ṣedeq is written in the supplication formulas in Text II-3 and IV in hand b (fols. 20vb, 22va; see also MM-001, fol. 153va).</persName>
